{"tid":490623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想畫聖誕卡","createTime":"2017-12-05T20:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T21:29:40.000Z","uid":34604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2faa97600d2e80f53eeb582a038bb564ed419a6f","tid":490623,"uid":34604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T20:01:23.000Z","msg":"有無人想收聖誕卡<br />\n如果你唔介意啲字同張卡可能會好肉酸既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就填Form啦！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/4ende0WdCjYXyyKE3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F4ende0WdCjYXyyKE3&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=608ae7eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/4ende0WdCjYXyyKE3</a><br />\n<br />\n名額不限，我會盡量趕工係聖誕前寄出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲咩心事/想我寫或者畫都可以同我講<br />\n懶得填Form既留Tg都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預祝各位聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f8f636787d44f119d69cc111ef865daf325e2b","tid":490623,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T20:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9978a7f598d537bdab12a11083a4544bb9ab421b","tid":490623,"uid":34604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T21:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>填左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw其實我標題係想打 好想寄聖誕卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6aec05620faf007fd36a157f69701b656f9c0b","tid":490623,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"填咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以的話就俾個回郵地址我啦，我想寄返俾你<img src=\"/as